<blockquote>
<p>This project was undertaken by&nbsp;IET and colleagues from the University of Southampton and is just completing its final report. The project's aim was to produce a synthesis of evidence based research which throws light on the progress made in the practice of Assessment and Feedback in H.E. This presentation will highlight findings with respect to authentic assessment, e-portfolios, peer assessment, feedback for language learning and Advice for Action.</p>
